{"tid":1561231,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[光復上水]   有街坊報警要求跟進火車站水貨客活動 反被點相","createTime":"2019-09-11T13:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T14:53:37.000Z","uid":299623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"036381808760e393980ae929c28d600dac81e4f0","tid":1561231,"uid":299623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:53:33.000Z","msg":"上水某街坊群組 發起每日報警趕水客<br />\n今晚大約0800左右 再有街坊報警 <br />\n0810 約10名警員到場<br />\n但我發現佢地到場竟然同水貨客好老友 <br />\n水客更將報警街坊大頭照 交比警員<br />\n其後有警員對住無人既空地影一將相<br />\n我懷疑佢想就咁交差  <br />\n<br />\n上水警察同水賊唔通有利益輸送?<br />\n我而家有D擔心果位街坊 大家有咩方法保護佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3HrHGY5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3HrHGY5.jpg&h=aec7c65d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z9tV1Y6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz9tV1Y6.jpg&h=402fd3fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YYuFtD6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYYuFtD6.jpg&h=ef96b5c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4abf42b378b25a5f85a79b48120ee289e7d9c4cd","tid":1561231,"uid":34869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:53:57.000Z","msg":"仲報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374736852bc4088841f6a28f35ce30ba6c63c9c9","tid":1561231,"uid":299623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"一張相 心急仔打錯"},{"pid":"1f29e9372b72b2c957751656e1f439d45cae2492","tid":1561231,"uid":299623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4abf42b378b25a5f85a79b48120ee289e7d9c4cd","tid":1561231,"uid":34869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:53:57.000Z","msg":"仲報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:54:35.000Z","msg":"我係路過街坊 個群組比較多中年和理非"},{"pid":"27b1de757bbdf9e188da41e212af466067508d24","tid":156123